node.text: Big Announcement: I have a Brand NEW TV show called My World coming out starting Monday August 30th on CBS Sports! This show will pair me up with some of the best athletes in the world and I’ll get to spend a day in their world participating in their sport. Then they get to come into my world and go fishing! Can’t wait for everyone to see this show! #myworld #fishingshow

node.title: NEW TV SHOW “My World” coming Mon. August 30th 9 PM on CBC Sports!

node.text: Last night to sign up for the Ike Foundation Pro Am this Sat. June 5th on the Upper Chesapeake Bay! First place wins a Basscat/Yamaha valued at over 30K and all the proceeds go towards kids fishing! Sign up at theikefoundation.org or SWIPE UP in my story! @theikefoundation

node.text: Big Announcement: I have a Brand NEW TV show called My World coming out starting Monday August 30th on CBS Sports! This show will pair me up with some of the best athletes in the world and I’ll get to spend a day in their world participating in their sport. Then they get to come into my world and go fishing! Can’t wait for everyone to see this show! #myworld #fishingshow
